Spit Fire	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:DracotaurRaceTrait.RaceTrait.SpecialAttack.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:A dracotaur can spit a glob of fire as a standard action. Once a dracotaur spits, it cannot spit again for 1 minute. The dracotaur's spittle is a sticky adhesive substance that ignites when exposed to air, much like alchemist's fire. This glob of fiery spittle is treated as a ranged touch attack with a range increment of 20 feet. A direct hit deals 2d6 points of fire damage. Every creature within 5 feet of the point where the spittle hits takes 1d4 points of fire damage from the splash. Unlike alchemist's fi re, a dracotaur's spittle does not continue to burn.	KEY:Dracotaur ~ Spit Fire									BONUS:VAR|SpitFire|2	BONUS:VAR|SpitFireDie|6								ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Spit Fire									SOURCEPAGE:MM3	
