Spiked Skin	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:DinosaurBloodstrikerRaceTrait.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:A bloodstriker's thick skin bristles with defensive spikes. Any creature attacking a bloodstriker with a melee weapon or natural weapon takes 1d8+6 points of piercing and slashing damage from the dinosaur's barbs. Weapons with exceptional reach, such as longspears, do not endanger their users in this way.	KEY:Dinosaur (Bloodstriker) ~ Spiked Skin																											SOURCEPAGE:MM3	
