Eye Rays	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:LurkingStranglerRaceTrait.SpecialAttack.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Each of a lurking strangler's two eye rays resembles a spell cast by a 3rd-level caster. One eye acts as the cause fear spell, and the other produces a sleep effect. Each effect is negated with a DC %1 Will save. The save DCs are Charisma-based. &nl; Cause Fear: This ray works like the spell. It has a range of 30 feet. &nl; Sleep: This ray works like the spell, except that it affects one creature with up to 4 Hit Dice. It has a range of 130 feet.|EyeRaysDC	KEY:Lurking Strangler ~ Eye Rays				DEFINE:EyeRaysDC|0					BONUS:VAR|EyeRaysDC|DefaultDCCha	BONUS:VAR|EyeRaysDC|2|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Ability Focus (Eye Rays)								ABILITY:Ability Focus|AUTOMATIC|Eye Rays									SOURCEPAGE:MM3	
